commit.message:
cfgcleanup.c, [...]: Update copyright.

	* cfgcleanup.c, df.h, diagnostic.c, rtl.c, tree-vectorizer.h,
	config/darwin7.h, config/mips/mips.c,
	config/rs6000/altivec.md, config/rs6000/darwin-tramp.asm:
	Update copyright.

From-SVN: r94704
